### Categorías

### GET all categories
GET http://localhost:5000/api/categories

### GET category by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/categories/1

### CREATE category
POST http://localhost:5000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alimentación",
  "description": "Gastos de comida y bebidas"
}

### UPDATE category
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alimentación",
  "description": "Gastos de comida, bebidas y restaurantes"
}

### DELETE (Deactivate) category
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/categories/1

### ACTIVATE category
POST http://localhost:5000/api/categories/1/activate

---

### Presupuestos

### GET all budgets
GET http://localhost:5000/api/budgets

### GET budget by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/budgets/1

### GET budgets by category
GET http://localhost:5000/api/budgets/category/1

### CREATE budget
POST http://localhost:5000/api/budgets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "monthlyAmount": 500.00,
  "month": 1,
  "year": 2024,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### UPDATE budget (only amount)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/budgets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "monthlyAmount": 600.00,
  "month": 1,
  "year": 2024,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### DELETE budget
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/budgets/1

---

### Gastos

### GET all expenses
GET http://localhost:5000/api/expenses

### GET expense by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/1

### GET expenses by budget
GET http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/budget/1

### GET expenses by period
GET http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/by-period/1/2024

### CREATE expense
POST http://localhost:5000/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Compra en supermercado",
  "amount": 45.50,
  "dateTime": "2024-01-15T14:30:00Z",
  "category": "Alimentación",
  "notes": "Compra semanal",
  "budgetId": 1
}

### CREATE expense without budget
POST http://localhost:5000/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Gasto adicional",
  "amount": 25.00,
  "dateTime": "2024-01-16T10:00:00Z",
  "category": null,
  "notes": "Gasto no presupuestado"
}

### DELETE expense
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/1

---

### Gastos Fijos

### GET all fixed expenses
GET http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses

### GET fixed expense by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses/1

### GET active fixed expenses
GET http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses/active

### GET fixed expenses by category
GET http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses/category/1

### CREATE fixed expense
POST http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Renta",
  "amount": 800.00,
  "chargeMonth": 1,
  "year": 2024,
  "chargeDay": 1,
  "description": "Alquiler del apartamento",
  "categoryId": null,
  "budgetId": null
}

### CREATE fixed expense with category
POST http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Internet",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "chargeMonth": 1,
  "year": 2024,
  "chargeDay": 5,
  "description": "Servicio de internet",
  "categoryId": 2,
  "budgetId": null
}

### UPDATE fixed expense
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Renta",
  "amount": 850.00,
  "chargeMonth": 1,
  "year": 2024,
  "chargeDay": 1,
  "description": "Alquiler del apartamento (actualizado)",
  "categoryId": null,
  "budgetId": null
}

### DELETE (Deactivate) fixed expense
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses/1

### ACTIVATE fixed expense
POST http://localhost:5000/api/fixedexpenses/1/activate

---

### Prueba Completa de Flujo

### 1. Crear categoría
POST http://localhost:5000/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Transporte",
  "description": "Gastos de transporte"
}

### 2. Crear presupuesto para la categoría
POST http://localhost:5000/api/budgets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "monthlyAmount": 200.00,
  "month": 1,
  "year": 2024,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### 3. Crear gasto dentro del presupuesto
POST http://localhost:5000/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Gasolina",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "dateTime": "2024-01-15T08:00:00Z",
  "category": "Transporte",
  "notes": "Gasolina para el auto",
  "budgetId": 1
}

### 4. Ver estado del presupuesto
GET http://localhost:5000/api/budgets/1

### 5. Ver todos los gastos del presupuesto
GET http://localhost:5000/api/expenses/budget/1
